('96280','33211','5','Romantic Finca in Santa Maria with marvellous view at the Tramuntana mountains'),
('96281','33212','5','The mansion from the year 1500 stands under conservation of monuments. The historic building was completely restored in 1995, receiving the authentic materials. Now is a time to renovate again to update with modern materials.The property is situated on a land of approx. 23.000 m² with fruit plantations and pine wood. The Finca was used like a hotel and disposes of 9 rustic and comfortably furnished rooms with baths en suite. Two other masters suites with private baths belong to the main living area. The living area with dining room, high-quality hotel kitchen, economic areas and guests WC is enough for the highest claims. About the generous terraces one reaches to the Mediterranean invested garden with pool area.'),
